mailtrace
=========

This project is a re-engineered re-implementation of the USPS first-class
mail envelope generator and Informed Visibility tracking service originally
published at https://github.com/1997cui/envelope (AGPL-3.0).

The Intelligent Mail Barcode (IMb) encoder in src/mailtrace/imb.py is
adapted from the original envelope project, which itself is a Python
implementation released by Sam Rushing under the Simplified BSD License
(see https://www.opensource.org/licenses/bsd-license.html).

The bundled font src/mailtrace/static/USPSIMBStandard.ttf is the
USPS-published Intelligent Mail Barcode font, distributed by USPS for
mailers' use.

